<br>
The Last Team Report for us was for 1.58.<br>
We ever going to get some Graphical effect or what not for Flurry and Dirty Tricks.  Or let me guess....there on the back burner like most things generally are.<br>
<br>
DW/CD compared to LA.  This issue ever going to be more then just Looked into and something actually done with it?<br>
<br>
Point of the Merc Class?  <br>
<br>
RvRing.  Charge is nice and all.  But Im tired of more buttons to push in order for my character to be brought up some.  Also...Charge is still going directly to Sprint.  <br>
Banging on the Doors are the only thing Mercs are good for.  We do more damage to the doors then most other classes since we have the chance to hit it with both wpns.  But thats as far as it goes.  Im not gonna switch to a shield so I can block an arrow once every blue moon.  Using a Ram any class can do for the most part so Im not even going to consider that as a Option.  On another note about Shields....Why bother being a Merc if you going to use a Shield?<br>
<br>
Parry/Shield- Both of these are still bugged in RvR.  When is this going to be completely fixed?<br>
<br>
Styles- There still the same ol boring things about those that need to be looked into.<br>
<br>
Realm Abilitys- Void.....Is usually A-voided at all cost.  Seen some mercs have it just to respec to get rid of it.<br>
Bladedance- Nice ability but How about bringing the Timer down to around 15 minutes.  Or reducing the cost?<br>
Rain of ?-  Havent seen ANYONE with these abilitys.  Could change there cost to 1,3,6 to make them more appealing.<br>
<br>
For the most part....Get DW/CD equal to that of LA at least.<br>
<br>
