onus to hit...No bonus to damage..and the styles we have that either slow or what not it breaks.  Defense is only good in PvE since as I stated above parry and shield still are bugged in RvR.  I can parry mobs like crazy.  But once I go up against an enemy player Id be lucky to parry once it seems.  To me and just about everyone else that I have talked to think that DW/CD/LA should all work the same.  I can understand that in real life different places to things differently.  But for common game play and game dynamics they would make them the same for balancing issues.<br>
<br>
Common day in the life of a Merc in RvR.<br>
<br>
MIDS INC!  <br>
-Mid- Insta mez<br>
-Merc- Damn Mezzed<br>
